description:
Ever wonder why Sybase Adaptive Server Enterprise is one of the best Relational Database Management system of the world.

This course will get you going with Sybase ASE 16.

In this course you will learn about Sybase installation on windows, Basic Administration and Backup/restore of Sybase ASE 16.

Big Financial companies use Sybase as their preferred platform of an RDBMS.

This course is designed for an absolute starters.

This course will help Seasoned Oracle/SQL Server/MySQL DBAs who also needs to support Sybase ASE.

You should take this course to start working on Sybase ASE without having any prior knowledge of Sybase ASE.
title: Get Started with SAP - Sybase ASE 16 On Windows
